parameters:
Ginga is absent from school today due to yesterday's fatigue. Let's
leave him be.

\C[17]et's head to the Meat Masa shop.\C[0] (The Meat Masa shop is
located south of Daimon Shopping Street.)
Yui quickly fixed up her appearance.
Ginga: "Did you manage to sleep well after that?"

Yui: "Somehow, even though it's a usual morning, I get embarrassed
when I meet you, Ginga"
Ginga: "That's exactly what I was about to say!"
Yui: "Feeling the same way, it makes me so happy♪"
Ginga: "Well then, shall we have breakfast?"
Yui: "Don't tell me he went to school without me!?"

Yui: "What the heck! We promised to go to school together today,
ugh!!"
